@startuml User_Account_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: User Account Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title User Account State Transitions

[*] --> Unverified : Registration

Unverified --> Email_Verified : Email confirmed
Unverified --> [*] : Expired (7 days)

Email_Verified --> Pending_KYC : Submit KYC documents
Email_Verified --> Limited_Access : Skip KYC (limited features)

Pending_KYC --> KYC_Review : Documents submitted
KYC_Review --> Active : KYC approved
KYC_Review --> KYC_Rejected : Documents invalid
KYC_Review --> Pending_KYC : Resubmit required

KYC_Rejected --> Pending_KYC : Resubmit documents
KYC_Rejected --> Limited_Access : Continue without KYC

Limited_Access --> Pending_KYC : Submit KYC later
Limited_Access --> Suspended : Policy violation

Active --> Suspended : Policy violation
Active --> Locked : Security issue
Active --> Inactive : No activity (180 days)

Suspended --> Active : Appeal approved
Suspended --> Banned : Appeal rejected

Locked --> Active : Security resolved
Locked --> Banned : Fraud confirmed

Inactive --> Active : User returns
Inactive --> Archived : Inactive (365 days)

Banned --> [*]
Archived --> [*]

note right of Limited_Access
  Restrictions:
  - Cannot withdraw funds
  - Limited program access
  - Lower trust score
end note

note right of Active
  Full access:
  - All features enabled
  - Can submit reports
  - Can withdraw funds
end note

note right of Suspended
  Temporary ban:
  - Cannot submit reports
  - Cannot access programs
  - Can appeal decision
end note

@enduml